====Noun====
{{en-noun}}

# One who [[abstain]]s; a [[faster]]. {{defdate|First attested around 1350 to 1470.}}<ref name=SOED/>
# {{context|usually|capitalized|religion|historical|lang=en}} One of a sect who appeared in France and Spain in the 3rd century, and believed in abstinence towards meat and sex.

